name: Fragile Gernady
description:
About:
Gernady is an ongoing art project where I fuse characterized grenades with pop culture. This isn't an everyday project but more of an ever growing art collection. Each piece will be unique in its subject matter and sometimes pose, location and accessories. At the end of the day this is a creative playground where Gernady is the star and plays dress up each and every night. Some pieces will be 1 of 1 and some will be edition based, these decisions will really be based on the subject matter and prices will vary based on all of these factors.
